## Section 2 — Complete Collection Inventory

| #  | Collection            | Purpose                                                        |
|----|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| 1  | users                 | All platform users across all roles and Studios               |
| 2  | userContexts          | Precomputed RBAC document per user                            |
| 3  | companies             | Organizations managing multiple Professionals                 |
| 4  | companyMembers        | Maps Professionals to Companies                               |
| 5  | professionalProfiles  | Extended profile for Professional-role users                  |
| 6  | professionalRelations | Professional to Individual relationship graph                 |
| 7  | cohorts               | Named groups of Individuals under a Professional              |
| 8  | cohortMembers         | Maps Individuals to Cohorts                                   |
| 9  | programs              | Learning programs / training courses / assessment tracks      |
| 10 | programModules        | Individual content units within a Program                     |
| 11 | programProgress       | Tracks Individual progress per Program module                 |
| 12 | tools                 | Assessment tools / skills evaluations / candidate assessments |
| 13 | toolQuestions         | Questions within a Tool                                       |
| 14 | toolSubmissions       | Individual's submitted answers for a Tool                     |
| 15 | toolResults           | Scored and processed results from a Tool submission           |
| 16 | assignments           | Core execution entity linking Individuals to Programs/Tools   |
| 17 | events                | Platform events, webinars, workshops, sessions                |
| 18 | eventRegistrations    | Individual registrations for Events                           |
| 19 | reports               | AI-generated branded PDF reports per Individual per Tool      |
| 20 | notifications         | In-app notification records per user                          |
| 21 | widgetSessions        | External widget usage sessions (anonymous + converted)        |
| 22 | auditLogs             | Immutable audit trail for all critical platform actions       |
| 23 | studioConfig          | Per-Studio runtime configuration overrides                    |
| 24 | marketplace           | Paid program and event listings for public discovery          |
| 25 | payments              | Payment transaction records (Stripe-linked)                   |

