| subscriptionTier   | enum      | YES      | enterprise / pro                                     |
| subscriptionStatus | enum      | YES      | active / trialing / past_due / cancelled             |
| stripeCustomerId   | string    | NO       | Stripe customer ID for billing                       |
| status             | enum      | YES      | active / suspended / archived                        |
| maxProfessionals   | number    | NO       | Seat limit (null = unlimited)                        |
| createdAt          | Timestamp | YES      | Company creation timestamp                           |
| updatedAt          | Timestamp | YES      | Last update timestamp                                |

