| linkedinUrl      | string    | NO       | LinkedIn profile URL                                   |
| widgetBaseUrl    | string    | NO       | Base URL for widget embedding                          |
| subscriptionTier | enum      | NO       | free / pro (if independent)                            |
| subscriptionStatus| enum     | NO       | active / trialing / past_due / cancelled               |
| stripeCustomerId | string    | NO       | Stripe customer ID (if independent billing)            |
| totalIndividuals | number    | YES      | Denormalized count of active Individuals               |
