### 3.6 professionalRelations
Purpose: The relationship graph between Professionals and their Individuals.

| Field          | Type      | Required | Description                                              |
|----------------|-----------|----------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| id             | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                               |
| studioType     | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                           |
| professionalId | string    | YES      | userId of the Professional                               |
| individualId   | string    | YES      | userId of the Individual                                 |
| companyId      | string    | NO       | Company context (if Professional is company-affiliated)  |
| source         | enum      | YES      | invited / csv_import / widget / marketplace / self_registered |
| status         | enum      | YES      | active / paused / archived                               |
| startedAt      | Timestamp | YES      | When the relationship became active                      |
| archivedAt     | Timestamp | NO       | When archived                                            |
| createdAt      | Timestamp | YES      | Record creation timestamp                                |

Indexes:
- (professionalId, status) — list all active Individuals for a Professional
- (individualId, studioType) — find which Professional an Individual belongs to
- (companyId, status) — aggregate all company relationships

