### 3.11 programProgress
Purpose: Tracks an Individual's completion status for each module within an assigned Program.

| Field              | Type      | Required | Description                                        |
|--------------------|-----------|----------|----------------------------------------------------|
| id                 | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                         |
| studioType         | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                     |
| userId             | string    | YES      | Individual's userId                                |
| programId          | string    | YES      | Reference to programs.id                          |
| moduleId           | string    | YES      | Reference to programModules.id                    |
| assignmentId       | string    | YES      | Reference to assignments.id                       |
| status             | enum      | YES      | locked / available / in_progress / completed       |
| progressPercentage | number    | YES      | 0-100, recalculated on each module completion      |
| startedAt          | Timestamp | NO       | When Individual first opened this module           |
| completedAt        | Timestamp | NO       | When Individual marked this module complete        |

Indexes:
- (userId, programId) — all module progress for a user within a program
- (assignmentId) — progress linked to specific assignment

