### 3.14 toolSubmissions
Purpose: Records an Individual's raw answers for a Tool attempt.

| Field         | Type      | Required | Description                                            |
|---------------|-----------|----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| id            | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                             |
| studioType    | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                         |
| toolId        | string    | YES      | Reference to tools.id                                 |
| userId        | string    | YES      | Individual's userId                                    |
| assignmentId  | string    | NO       | Reference to assignments.id (null if self-initiated)  |
| professionalId| string    | NO       | Individual's Professional (denormalized)               |
| attemptNumber | number    | YES      | 1 for first attempt, increments on retry               |
| answers       | map       | YES      | Map of { questionId: answer } — raw submitted answers  |
| status        | enum      | YES      | in_progress / submitted / processed                    |
| startedAt     | Timestamp | YES      | When Individual opened the tool                        |
| submittedAt   | Timestamp | NO       | When Individual submitted answers                      |
| processedAt   | Timestamp | NO       | When scoring was completed                             |

Indexes:
- (userId, toolId) — all submission attempts for a user on a tool
- (assignmentId) — submission linked to a specific assignment

