### 3.15 toolResults
Purpose: Scored and processed results from a Tool submission. Supports longitudinal tracking.

| Field           | Type      | Required | Description                                          |
|-----------------|-----------|----------|------------------------------------------------------|
| id              | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                           |
| studioType      | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                       |
| toolId          | string    | YES      | Reference to tools.id                               |
| userId          | string    | YES      | Individual's userId                                  |
| submissionId    | string    | YES      | Reference to toolSubmissions.id                     |
| professionalId  | string    | NO       | Denormalized Professional reference                  |
| overallScore    | number    | YES      | Composite score (0-100 or tool-defined scale)        |
| dimensionScores | map       | YES      | Map of { dimensionName: score }                      |
| interpretation  | string    | NO       | Score label (e.g. High Clarity, Developing)          |
| reportId        | string    | NO       | Reference to reports.id (after report generation)   |
| createdAt       | Timestamp | YES      | When result was computed                             |

Indexes:
- (userId, toolId, createdAt) — longitudinal result history
