| generatedAt            | Timestamp | YES      | When report was generated                          |

Indexes:
- (userId, toolId, generatedAt) — Individual's report history for a tool
- (userId, studioType, generatedAt) — all reports for an Individual
- (professionalId, generatedAt) — Professional's report delivery history

---

### 3.20 notifications
Purpose: In-app notification records for every platform user.

| Field             | Type      | Required | Description                                          |
|-------------------|-----------|----------|------------------------------------------------------|
| id                | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                           |
| studioType        | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                       |
| userId            | string    | YES      | Recipient's userId                                   |
| type              | enum      | YES      | assignment_created / assignment_completed / assignment_overdue / report_ready / event_reminder / event_registration / program_unlocked / platform_announcement |
| title             | string    | YES      | Short notification title                             |
| message           | string    | YES      | Full notification message body                       |
| actionUrl         | string    | NO       | Deep link URL within the app                         |
| relatedEntityType | string    | NO       | assignment / report / event / program / tool         |
| relatedEntityId   | string    | NO       | ID of the related entity                             |
| isRead            | boolean   | YES      | Whether user has read this notification              |
| readAt            | Timestamp | NO       | When user read this notification                     |
| createdAt         | Timestamp | YES      | When notification was created                        |

Indexes:
- (userId, isRead, createdAt) — unread notifications for a user
- (userId, studioType, createdAt) — full notification history

---

### 3.21 widgetSessions
Purpose: Tracks external website assessment completions — anonymous and converted users.

| Field           | Type      | Required | Description                                            |
|-----------------|-----------|----------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| id              | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                             |
| studioType      | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                         |
| toolId          | string    | YES      | Reference to tools.id being taken                     |
| professionalId  | string    | YES      | Professional whose widget was embedded                 |
| anonymousId     | string    | YES      | Browser-generated anonymous session ID                 |
| emailCaptured   | string    | NO       | Email entered after tool completion                    |
| status          | enum      | YES      | started / completed / email_captured / converted       |
| convertedUserId | string    | NO       | userId if anonymous user registered                    |
| submissionId    | string    | NO       | Reference to toolSubmissions.id                       |
| sourceUrl       | string    | NO       | External URL where the widget was embedded             |
| startedAt       | Timestamp | YES      | Session start timestamp                                |
| completedAt     | Timestamp | NO       | Completion timestamp                                   |
| convertedAt     | Timestamp | NO       | When anonymous user registered                         |

Indexes:
- (professionalId, status) — Professional's widget lead funnel
- (studioType, status) — platform-wide widget conversion analytics

---

### 3.22 auditLogs
Purpose: Immutable audit trail. Written exclusively by Firebase Functions. Never updated or deleted.

| Field         | Type      | Required | Description                                              |
|---------------|-----------|----------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| id            | string    | YES      | Auto-generated document ID                               |
| studioType    | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                           |
| actorId       | string    | YES      | userId of the person who performed the action            |
| actorRole     | string    | YES      | Role at time of action                                   |
| action        | string    | YES      | Action identifier (e.g. user.role_changed, assignment.created) |
| entityType    | string    | YES      | Type of entity affected (user, assignment, report)       |
| entityId      | string    | YES      | ID of the entity affected                                |
| previousState | map       | NO       | Snapshot of entity state before change                   |
| newState      | map       | NO       | Snapshot of entity state after change                    |
| metadata      | map       | NO       | Additional context (IP address, device type)             |
| createdAt     | Timestamp | YES      | Immutable action timestamp                               |

Indexes:
- (studioType, action, createdAt) — audit log filtering
- (actorId, createdAt) — all actions by a specific user
- (entityType, entityId) — audit history for a specific entity

---

### 3.23 marketplace
Purpose: Public-facing listings of paid Programs and Events for self-directed purchase.

| Field         | Type      | Required | Description                                        |
|---------------|-----------|----------|----------------------------------------------------|
| id            | string    | YES      | Same as programs.id or events.id                  |
| studioType    | enum      | YES      | Studio context                                     |
| entityType    | enum      | YES      | program / event                                    |
| entityId      | string    | YES      | Reference to programs.id or events.id             |
| title         | string    | YES      | Denormalized title                                 |
| description   | string    | YES      | Denormalized short description                     |
| coverImageUrl | string    | NO       | Denormalized cover image                           |
| price         | number    | YES      | Listing price                                      |
| currency      | string    | YES      | ISO currency code                                  |
| createdBy     | string    | YES      | userId of creator (for revenue attribution)        |
| totalSales    | number    | YES      | Denormalized sales count                           |
| rating        | number    | NO       | Average rating (future)                            |
| status        | enum      | YES      | active / paused / removed                          |
| listedAt      | Timestamp | YES      | When listed in marketplace                         |
| updatedAt     | Timestamp | YES      | Last update                                        |

