| currency             | string    | YES      | ISO currency code                                  |
| status               | enum      | YES      | pending / succeeded / failed / refunded            |
| stripePaymentIntentId| string    | YES      | Stripe Payment Intent ID                           |
| stripeCustomerId     | string    | NO       | Stripe Customer ID of the buyer                    |
| platformFee          | number    | NO       | StudioVerse commission amount                      |
