## Section 4 — Entity Relationship Model

StudioVerse (studioType = tenant boundary)
│
├── SuperAdmin
│   ├── manages → users (all roles)
│   ├── creates → programs (platform-owned)
│   ├── creates → tools (platform-owned)
│   ├── creates → events (global)
│   └── reads → auditLogs, analytics
│
├── Company
│   ├── has many → companyMembers (Professionals)
│   ├── has many → cohorts (company-level)
│   └── sees aggregate → assignments, reports (own Professionals only)
│
├── Professional (independent or company-affiliated)
│   ├── has many → professionalRelations (Individuals)
│   ├── has many → cohorts
│   │   └── has many → cohortMembers (Individuals)
│   ├── creates → assignments (Programs + Tools to Individuals/Cohorts)
│   ├── creates → events (private)
│   ├── creates → programs (own library)
│   ├── deploys → tools (via widget or assignment)
│   └── receives → reports (own Individuals only)
│
├── Individual
│   ├── has many → assignments
│   │   ├── linked to → programs → programModules → programProgress
│   │   └── linked to → tools → toolSubmissions → toolResults → reports
│   ├── has many → eventRegistrations → events
│   └── owns → notifications
│
├── Tool
│   ├── has many → toolQuestions
│   ├── has many → toolSubmissions (per user per attempt)
│   │   └── has one → toolResult → report
│   └── may be deployed via → widgetSessions (external)
│
└── Assignment (core execution entity)
    ├── links → Professional to Individual
    ├── links → resource (program or tool)
    ├── tracks → status lifecycle
    └── triggers → notifications

---

## Section 5 — Query Patterns

| Use Case                        | Collection          | Query                                                      |
|---------------------------------|---------------------|------------------------------------------------------------|
| Individual's pending assignments | assignments        | where userId == X, where status == assigned                |
| Professional's cohort progress  | assignments         | where assignedBy == X, where cohortId == Y                 |
| Expand cohort to members        | cohortMembers       | where cohortId == X, where status == active                |
| Individual's program progress   | programProgress     | where userId == X, where programId == Y                    |
| Individual's tool result history| toolResults         | where userId == X, where toolId == Y, orderBy createdAt    |
| All reports for an Individual   | reports             | where userId == X, orderBy generatedAt                     |
| Global event discovery          | events              | where studioType == X, where visibility == global, where status == published, orderBy startDate |
| Unread notifications            | notifications       | where userId == X, where isRead == false, orderBy createdAt|
| Widget conversion funnel        | widgetSessions      | where professionalId == X, where status == converted       |
| Marketplace catalog             | marketplace         | where studioType == X, where status == active, orderBy listedAt |
| Audit trail for entity          | auditLogs           | where entityType == X, where entityId == Y, orderBy createdAt |

---

