| assignments          | (assignedBy, status)                      | Professional's assignment view   |
| assignments          | (cohortId, resourceId)                    | Duplicate assignment check       |
| assignments          | (studioType, status, deadline)            | Overdue detection                |
| events               | (studioType, visibility, status, startDate)| Global event discovery          |
