| eventRegistrations   | (eventId, status)                         | Event attendee list              |
| eventRegistrations   | (userId, studioType)                      | Individual's registrations       |
| reports              | (userId, toolId, generatedAt)             | Tool report history              |
| reports              | (professionalId, generatedAt)             | Professional's report log        |
| notifications        | (userId, isRead, createdAt)               | Unread notification badge        |
| widgetSessions       | (professionalId, status)                  | Widget funnel analytics          |
| auditLogs            | (studioType, action, createdAt)           | Audit filtering                  |
| auditLogs            | (entityType, entityId)                    | Entity audit history             |
| marketplace          | (studioType, status, listedAt)            | Marketplace catalog              |

