## Section 7 — Multi-Tenancy Data Rules

The studioType field is set at document creation time by Firebase Functions. It is immutable after creation. All queries include studioType as the first filter.

Isolation Rules:
- SuperAdmin: full read across Studios with explicit studioType filter; no cross-tenant write
- Company: sees all Professionals and Individuals in their companyId scope only
- Professional: sees own Individuals, cohorts, assignments, reports only — not other Professionals' data
- Individual: sees own profile, assignments, programs, tools, reports only

Independent Professional Rule:
- companyId is null on all their documents
- isIndependent = true in userContexts
- Data isolated by professionalId alone

userContext Integrity:
- Must be rebuilt within 30 seconds of any relationship change
- UI must not cache userContext beyond current session
- If userContexts/{userId} does not exist → treat as unauthenticated → redirect to login
- SuperAdmin may trigger manual buildUserContext for any user

---

## Section 8 — Data Lifecycle and Retention

| Collection       | Retention Rule                                                          |
|------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| users            | Retained indefinitely; archived status used instead of deletion         |
| assignments      | Retained indefinitely — immutable execution record                      |
| toolSubmissions  | Retained indefinitely — answers part of longitudinal profile            |
| toolResults      | Retained indefinitely — core data asset                                 |
| reports          | PDF archived after 2 years; document retained indefinitely              |
| auditLogs        | Retained indefinitely — never deleted                                   |
| notifications    | Soft-deleted after 90 days (isRead + age > 90 days)                    |
| widgetSessions   | Retained 12 months; anonymized after conversion or expiry              |
| payments         | Retained 7 years (financial compliance)                                 |
| programProgress  | Retained indefinitely — part of Individual's growth record              |

---

## Section 9 — Security Rules Summary

| Collection           | Read                                          | Write         |
|----------------------|-----------------------------------------------|---------------|
| users                | Own document only                             | Functions only|
| userContexts         | Own document only                             | Functions only|
| companies            | Company members only                          | Functions only|
| companyMembers       | Company admin + own record                    | Functions only|
| professionalProfiles | Own + their Individuals (limited)             | Functions only|
| professionalRelations| Professional (own) + Individual (own)         | Functions only|
| cohorts              | Owning Professional + company admin           | Functions only|
| cohortMembers        | Owning Professional + Individual (own)        | Functions only|
| programs             | Any authenticated user                        | Functions only|
| programModules       | Any authenticated user                        | Functions only|
| programProgress      | Own userId only                               | Functions only|
| tools                | Any authenticated user                        | Functions only|
| toolQuestions        | Any authenticated user                        | Functions only|
| toolSubmissions      | Own userId + assigned Professional            | Functions only|
| toolResults          | Own userId + assigned Professional            | Functions only|
| assignments          | Own userId + assignedBy Professional          | Functions only|
| events               | Authenticated users (global) / own (private)  | Functions only|
| eventRegistrations   | Own userId + event creator                    | Functions only|
| reports              | Own userId + assigned Professional            | Functions only|
| notifications        | Own userId only                               | Functions only|
| widgetSessions       | Owning Professional only                      | Functions only|
| auditLogs            | SuperAdmin only                               | Functions only|
| marketplace          | Any authenticated user                        | Functions only|
| payments             | Own userId + SuperAdmin                       | Functions only|

